    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345760/extras/b090c5746cc6388bc71df47e5803016c.poster.avif?t=1768229725\" width=616 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345760/extras/b090c5746cc6388bc71df47e5803016c.webm?t=1768229725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345760/extras/b090c5746cc6388bc71df47e5803016c.mp4?t=1768229725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>《Matchpoint – Tennis Championships》</strong>是一个现代的流行网球游戏，深度的职业生涯模式和独特的对抗系统为玩家来带逼真的球场体验。<br><br>这款游戏非常注重战术真实感、定位和瞄准，让玩家以正确的方式操控超级网球巨星的步法，以最大限度地发挥出进球优势。<br><br><strong>《Matchpoint – Tennis Championships》</strong>结合了巧妙的角色动画、真实的网球力学，同时还改善了玩家操控体验，完美复制了网球比赛中的现实节奏 - 每一次挥拍和击球都让人感觉独特而满意。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345760/extras/4d8f0c48418f6b962245b6a7d8e4ea69.webp?t=1768229725\" width=19 height=19 /></span> 进入职业网球的世界</h2>&quot;Matchpoint - Tennis Championships &quot;提供了一个深入的职业模式，具有独特的基于功绩的排名系统。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345760/extras/4d8f0c48418f6b962245b6a7d8e4ea69.webp?t=1768229725\" width=19 height=19 /></span> 创建属于你自己的 3D 网球明星</h2>通过一组自定义选项选择你的外形，服装和游戏风格，包括真实的比赛技能，如左手或右手握拍，单手或双手反手击球。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345760/extras/4d8f0c48418f6b962245b6a7d8e4ea69.webp?t=1768229725\" width=19 height=19 /></span> 作为一名职业网球选手主导球场</h2>《Matchpoint – Tennis Championships》设置了 16 位来自真实职业巡回赛的国际网球明星，包括尼克·克耶高斯、锦织圭、阿曼达·阿尼西莫娃。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345760/extras/4d8f0c48418f6b962245b6a7d8e4ea69.webp?t=1768229725\" width=19 height=19 /></span> 熟练掌握所有挥拍和击球技巧</h2>通过选择当时最高水平的技巧来决定一场比赛的结果：上旋、平拍、挑拍或切拍。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345760/extras/4d8f0c48418f6b962245b6a7d8e4ea69.webp?t=1768229725\" width=19 height=19 /></span> 在离线或在线比赛中与对手一较高下</h2>与狡猾的人工智能机器人比赛，或者通过本地会话和在线联机在球场上直面你的朋友和对手。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345760/extras/4d8f0c48418f6b962245b6a7d8e4ea69.webp?t=1768229725\" width=19 height=19 /></span> 学习对手的动作和战术</h2>观察你的对手，了解他们的优势和劣势，在上场之前就获得战术优势。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345760/extras/4d8f0c48418f6b962245b6a7d8e4ea69.webp?t=1768229725\" width=19 height=19 /></span> 熟能生巧：请以为私人教练来打磨你的球技</h2>通过个人训练模块中的游戏内教练系统来增强你的优势，减少你的弱点。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345760/extras/4d8f0c48418f6b962245b6a7d8e4ea69.webp?t=1768229725\" width=19 height=19 /></span> 在练习和迷你游戏模式中调整你的战术</h2>加入大量迷你游戏，磨练你的完美技能，成为球场上不可小觑的力量。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345760/extras/4d8f0c48418f6b962245b6a7d8e4ea69.webp?t=1768229725\" width=19 height=19 /></span> 在世界各地的大型比赛场地进行表演赛</h2>每座球场都各有特色，研究你的比赛场地，以适应草地、红土和硬地球场的环境。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345760/extras/4d8f0c48418f6b962245b6a7d8e4ea69.webp?t=1768229725\" width=19 height=19 /></span> 回放模式</h2>破发点或决定性赛点，用影片记录你最激烈的比赛瞬间，并通过研究比赛结果来提升你的竞技表现。",
